What did Tin tell you?

109
00:10:04,685 --> 00:10:06,366
All the bad things you've done, obviously.

110
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,399
And you believed him?

111
00:10:09,297 --> 00:10:12,540
Yeah. Whatever Tin says,
I'll always believe him.

112
00:10:16,436 --> 00:10:19,258
