what Tin is thinking.

116
00:10:29,345 --> 00:10:30,658
Don't you dare insult Tin.

117
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:38,182
I won't believe anyone other than Tin.

118
00:10:39,182 --> 00:10:40,214
Remember that.

119
00:10:49,844 --> 00:10:51,002
What a waste.

120
00:10:54,083 --> 00:10:55,725
He acts just like Phu.

121
00:11:12,981 --> 00:11:17,734
Frigging' Champ, why don't you
just say that I already lost...

122
00:11:17,814 --> 00:11:18,901
Techno!

123
00:11:19,490 --> 00:11:21,533
Speaking of the devil
and the devil appears...

124
00:11:22,103 --> 00:11:23,207
I won't be here anymore.

125
00:11:26,192 --> 00:11:27,600
-Are you okay?
-Stop!

126
00:11:30,697 --> 00:11:31,918
Don't say anything.

127
00:11:33,071 --> 00:11:34,362
But...

128
00:11:34,442 --> 00:11:35,735
I said shut up!

129
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,435
If you say one more word,

130
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,027
I won't talk to you anymore.

131
00:11:44,849 --> 00:11:46,155
I'm embarrassed.

132
00:11:51,482 --> 00:11:52,503
Don't touch me.

133
00:12:00,293 --> 00:12:03,516
You're still cute even when you're angry.

134
00:12:09,623 --> 00:12:11,731
Come on Tin,
I'm just here to buy something with Ae.

135
00:12:11,811 --> 00:12:14,778
I'm just here to buy something with Ae.

136
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:20,965
And since exams are finished,
I just want to go shopping and relax.

137
00:12:21,911 --> 00:12:23,990
I'm not angry about that.

138
00:12:27,523 --> 00:12:30,558
Then you're angry that I'm here with Ae?

139
00:12:33,412 --> 00:12:36,190
Tin... It's just Ae.

140
00:12:38,588 --> 00:12:40,025
My spoiled prince,

141
00:12:40,501 --> 00:12:43,614
you know fully well who Ae likes.

142
00:12:45,672 --> 00:12:47,510
But I guess I can't really say much,

143
00:12:47,590 --> 00:12:49,615
since you also like me.

144
00:12:50,186 --> 00:12:52,662
Sorry that I'm very charming.

145
00:12:52,742 --> 00:12:55,104
I'm not surprised
if you get jealous over me.

146
00:12:55,184 --> 00:12:56,972
I'll make it up to you when I get back.

147
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:01,503
I gotta go, see you later.

148
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:08,106
I have an hour left...

149
00:13:08,571 --> 00:13:10,364
What should I do?

150
00:13:12,242 --> 00:13:13,409
Let's find something to eat.

151
00:13:15,201 --> 00:13:16,339
I'm not scared of you.

152
00:13:17,062 --> 00:13:18,443
What a coincidence.

153
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,381
What a coincidence my ass!

154
00:13:21,461 --> 00:13:23,112
Your house is in the opposite direction!

155
00:13:23,192 --> 00:13:24,356
Why are you here?

156
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,945
Fine, fine.

157
00:13:27,127 --> 00:13:28,643
I'm here to see you, Can.

158
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,114
Why?

159
00:13:32,512 --> 00:13:35,617
If you wanna know, let's talk for a bit.

160
00:14:03,082 --> 00:14:04,253
What are you looking at?

161
00:14:06,572 --> 00:14:08,211
You act just like a child.

162
00:14:08,698 --> 00:14:10,884
I didn't think
Tin would like someone like you.

163
00:14:11,704 --> 00:14:13,064
What's wrong with being like this?

164
00:14:15,396 --> 00:14:16,428
Nothing.

165
00:14:16,508 --> 00:14:18,532
I didn't mean anything bad.

166
00:14:19,534 --> 00:14:23,486
I'm just surprised
Tin is dating someone so innocent.

167
00:14:23,812 --> 00:14:26,116
Because in the past,
he didn't date people like this.

168
00:14:28,551 --> 00:14:29,781
Are you...

169
00:14:31,172 --> 00:14:33,410
trying to make me suspicious of Tin?

170
00:14:33,922 --> 00:14:34,974
Keep dreaming.

171
00:14:35,395 --> 00:14:36,879
The past doesn't mean anything.

172
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,763
I'm the present.

173
00:14:39,791 --> 00:14:41,288
I'm not here to do that.

174
00:14:41,836 --> 00:14:43,682
I'm just here
to correct a misunderstanding.

175
00:14:44,967 --> 00:14:46,034
To correct...

176
00:14:46,530 --> 00:14:47,696
a misunderstanding?

177
00:14:50,034 --> 00:14:53,029
Tin said
I accused him of taking drugs, right?

178
00:14:54,161 --> 00:14:57,152
It's not accusing
if he's telling the truth.

179
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:10,298
What...

180
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,603
is this?

181
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:18,986
Tin didn't tell you
that he did drugs before?

182
00:15:32,994 --> 00:15:34,134
Ae.

183
00:15:35,217 --> 00:15:37,137
I can't meet up with you today anymore.

184
00:15:37,217 --> 00:15:38,317
Sorry.

185
00:15:42,986 --> 00:15:44,230
About what you said.

186
00:15:44,816 --> 00:15:46,057
What did you mean?

187
00:15:54,998 --> 00:15:56,369
Here's your order.

188
00:15:56,449 --> 00:15:57,703
Thank you.

189
00:15:59,392 --> 00:16:01,407
