190
00:16:01,788 --> 00:16:02,878
Don't be so nosy.

191
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:05,276
Fine.

192
00:16:05,742 --> 00:16:09,603
Insult me as much as you want.

193
00:16:09,683 --> 00:16:12,708
It's all you do anyway.

194
00:16:14,667 --> 00:16:17,406
If you're not nosy,
why would you follow me then?

195
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:27,197
Sorry for the interruption.

196
00:16:27,277 --> 00:16:28,485
Let's talk.

197
00:16:28,565 --> 00:16:30,683
This is Ae
from the Faculty of Engineering.

198
00:16:30,763 --> 00:16:32,617
The one that I told you about before.

199
00:16:32,697 --> 00:16:33,889
And this is my friend.

200
00:16:33,969 --> 00:16:34,984
Tum.

201
00:16:35,631 --> 00:16:38,802
The one who wants an inspiration
for writing a song.

202
00:16:38,882 --> 00:16:41,620
That's why we're interested in your story.

203
00:16:43,793 --> 00:16:45,244
It's just you who's interested.

204
00:16:46,238 --> 00:16:48,402
Try talking to him first.

205
00:16:48,482 --> 00:16:50,782
Maybe you'll get some inspiration
for multiple songs.

206
00:16:50,862 --> 00:16:52,252
Not just one.

207
