211
00:17:08,388 --> 00:17:09,494
Stop it.

212
00:17:10,127 --> 00:17:11,557
I'm just stating the truth.

213
00:17:17,668 --> 00:17:19,174
Then let me ask you something.

214
00:17:19,254 --> 00:17:22,091
How interesting
do you think your story is?

215
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,247
I don't know.

216
00:17:28,120 --> 00:17:29,361
I just...

217
00:17:30,598 --> 00:17:33,158
know that I'm willing to do anything
to tell him that I love him.

218
00:17:35,121 --> 00:17:36,473
And I'll always be waiting.

219
00:17:42,331 --> 00:17:43,435
And what did he say?

220
00:17:48,066 --> 00:17:49,947
Have you ever loved someone so much?

221
00:17:51,707 --> 00:17:54,027
But there's something that
makes you unable to be together?

222
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,769
Of course.

223
00:18:05,413 --> 00:18:06,336
See?

224
00:18:06,416 --> 00:18:10,150
I told you that Ae's story is interesting.

225
00:18:10,893 --> 00:18:11,974
Yeah.

226
00:18:12,054 --> 00:18:14,734
I think it's already worth it
that we skipped practice to come here.

227
00:18:26,708 --> 00:18:28,219
-Hey, Ae.
-Shut up.

228
00:18:28,299 --> 00:18:29,448
I don't want to hear it.

229
00:18:30,589 --> 00:18:31,887
Fuck you.

230
00:18:31,967 --> 00:18:34,162
Why are you so rude?

231
00:18:34,549 --> 00:18:36,572
If you stop prying
into other people's businesses,

232
00:18:36,652 --> 00:18:38,496
maybe your life would be better.

233
00:18:38,576 --> 00:18:40,672
It's not like I can help it!

234
00:18:40,752 --> 00:18:42,132
Like that couple back there.

235
00:18:42,212 --> 00:18:43,846
Something smells fishy.

236
00:18:43,926 --> 00:18:45,239
Trust me.

237
00:18:45,319 --> 00:18:46,938
I can feel it.

238
00:18:47,535 --> 00:18:49,521
Keen likes Tum,

239
00:18:49,963 --> 00:18:51,824
but Tum likes someone else.

240
00:18:52,162 --> 00:18:53,387
